{"tid":1375043,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"比較721同727黑警執法,執你老母法啊","createTime":"2019-07-28T03:07:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T04:22:48.000Z","uid":271410,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5e1a85630a52ba5e0373ca303cc7b4a908d98b73","tid":1375043,"uid":271410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:07:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">721</span></span><br />\n<br />\n新界北總區重案組昨晚及今日分別於元朗、屯門及機場區再拘捕5名本地男子，年齡介乎39至51歲，<span style=\"color: red;\">涉嫌非法集結</span>，所有被捕男子現正被扣留調查，至今警方共<span style=\"color: red;\">拘捕11人</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190723/59853326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190723%2F59853326&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=dd747f36\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190723%2F59853326&h=594863af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190723/59853326</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">727 </span></span><br />\n【Now新聞台】大批市民在警方反對遊行的情況下到元朗聚集，期間多次與警方爆發衝突，警方入夜再次推進清場，主要將示威者集中在元朗西鐵站，警員更一度衝入西鐵站，以警棍打示威者，期間有人受傷，而在約晚上十一時，示威者陸續散去。警方拘捕<span style=\"color: red;\">11名男子</span>，年齡介乎18至68歲，<span style=\"color: red;\">涉嫌非法集結、藏有攻擊性武器、襲警及襲擊</span>等。<br />\n<br />\n大約晚上七時，警方黑旗示警，在元朗大馬路開始驅散，示威者往元朗西鐵站方向後退，警員一路推進，一路拆除路障，示威者一直退到西鐵站近南邊圍村。<br />\n<br />\n另一批示威者在南邊圍村及西邊圍村外跟警方對峙，有人向村口投擲冒煙物品，警員同樣將示威者迫向西鐵站。警方不斷推進，施放楜椒噴霧，現場有私家車遭毀壞，車內有長藤條等物品。部分示威者仍佔據朗業街一帶。<br />\n<br />\n至晚上九時半左右，警方再施放催淚彈，從多方面推進，將示威者驅趕上元朗西鐵站，有人倒地，接受急救，示威者及警員之間築起人鏈。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357010\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357010&d=GsYKB4iL2zhb3369BxXbpxAEDuEYyIgqOvZcTDxqS2A%3D&h=8efed517\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D357010&h=4ba64f11\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=357010</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">721用3日11個, charge 最輕<br />\n721一晚已經11個, charge 咁L多野</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">DLLM, 黑警死全家</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d8d23a56802b11255273641f2029c5cc5b1d8cd5","tid":1375043,"uid":267410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:10:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b26c826e596878de7027ab7752948d6df768386","tid":1375043,"uid":171192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T03:10:39.000Z","msg":"尋晚單野國際輿論無721咁正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n因為前日機場阿伯單野畀海外黨媒宣傳成&quot;香港示威者bully阿伯&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，仲要好多外國人信，事實係阿伯推撞人在先而大家唔俾佢搞完事就逃走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（唔肯定有無打人）<br />\n<br />\n依家有人將國際輿論方向帶緊去&ldquo;香港示威者失控所以警察先暴力對付&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n文宣們一齊出手喇！澄清返前日機場單野同尋日元朗單野！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b72969c819f19ac21eef554e0c444c625aa16321","tid":1375043,"uid":271410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T04:22:48.000Z","msg":"push"}]}